data.name: Energy.Fire.Description
data.value: Intense heat that quickly burns flammable materials and spreads destruction.

data.name: Gas.Corruption.Description
data.value: Gaseous corruption that spreads and contaminates the environment, making it inhospitable.

data.name: Gas.Smoke.Description
data.value: Smoke from burning, rises slowly and darkens the air, showing fire is present.

data.name: Gas.Steam.Description
data.value: Hot water vapor that rises rapidly and disperses in the air. At high altitudes, it can turn into clouds.

data.name: Liquid.Acid.Description
data.value: Corrosive liquid that quickly dissolves many materials on contact.

data.name: Liquid.Corruption.Description
data.value: Contaminating liquid that flows and corrupts everything it touches.

data.name: Liquid.Lava.Description
data.value: Molten rock that burns almost everything it touches. It cools and hardens when exposed to cold.

data.name: Liquid.Water.Description
data.value: Essential liquid that can freeze, evaporate, and put out fires.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.Corruption.Description
data.value: Crystallized, immobile corruption that creates permanent contaminated areas.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.Glass.Description
data.value: Transparent and fragile material, breaks with heat or impact.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.Iron.Description
data.value: Strong metal, resists fire but melts in lava.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.MountingBlock.Description
data.value: Decorative and functional block, flammable, used in mobile constructions.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.RedBrick.Description
data.value: Durable block, ideal for fire-resistant constructions.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.TreeLeaf.Description
data.value: Natural, flammable leaf, used for decoration.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.Wood.Description
data.value: Natural, very flammable material, common in constructions.

data.name: Solid.Movable.Corruption.Description
data.value: Substance that spreads, contaminates, and destroys the environment continuously.

data.name: Solid.Movable.Dirt.Description
data.value: Dry, unstable soil, base for vegetation. Turns into mud when in contact with water.

data.name: Solid.Movable.Grass.Description
data.value: Dry grass, very flammable, burns fast and leaves ash.

data.name: Solid.Movable.Ice.Description
data.value: Solid, slippery water, melts easily with heat.

data.name: Solid.Movable.Mud.Description
data.value: Mix of dirt and water, turns into dry dirt when heated.

data.name: Solid.Movable.Sand.Description
data.value: Mineral grains that flow and pile up. Become glass with extreme heat.

data.name: Solid.Movable.Snow.Description
data.value: Snowflakes that melt into water with heat.

data.name: Solid.Movable.Stone.Description
data.value: Rock that resists impacts, melts into lava with extreme heat or turns into sand with erosion.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.Lamp.Description
data.value: Fixed, sturdy lamp used for decoration.

data.name: Solid.Movable.Salt.Description
data.value: White, crystalline powder that dissolves in water.

data.name: Liquid.Oil.Description
data.value: Dark, thick, very flammable liquid with low density.

data.name: Liquid.Saltwater.Description
data.value: Light blue liquid with floating salt particles.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.DrySponge.Description
data.value: Dry sponge that absorbs liquids and is very flammable.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.WetSponge.Description
data.value: Wet sponge, denser and harder to burn. Dries with heat and moves down if dry sponges are below.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.Gold.Description
data.value: Bright yellow, soft, and malleable metal.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.Heater.Description
data.value: Device that heats all nearby elements.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.Freezer.Description
data.value: Device that cools all nearby elements.

data.name: Solid.Movable.Bomb.Description
data.value: Low-power bomb that explodes when hitting other elements.

data.name: Solid.Movable.Dynamite.Description
data.value: Large-radius explosive, only explodes with heat or contact with lava/fire.

data.name: Solid.Movable.TNT.Description
data.value: Moderate explosive, destroys solids and leaves smoke/fire. Only explodes with heat or contact with lava/fire.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.Void.Description
data.value: Absorbs and destroys everything it touches.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.Clone.Description
data.value: Infinitely generates the neighboring element until removed.

data.name: Solid.Movable.Ash.Description
data.value: Dark gray powder, looks like remains of wood or burnt materials.

data.name: Gas.AntiCorruption.Description
data.value: A gaseous antidote that attempts, by all means, to contain the destruction caused by corruption and restore the environment to its original state.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.Devourer.Description
data.value: It will try to consume everything around it. When it has nothing left to feed on, it will explode.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.LeftwardPusher.Description
data.value: Shifts neighboring elements to the left.

data.name: Solid.Immovable.RightwardPusher.Description
data.value: Shifts neighboring elements to the right.

data.name: Gas.ChargedCloud.Description
data.value: A dense, saturated cloud formed from the clustering of multiple clouds. When concentrated enough, it releases water or snow depending on temperature.
